50:21.208 --> 50:23.458
of the prowler
seen this morning.

50:23.542 --> 50:26.125
Send a marked unit to the area.

50:26.208 --> 50:28.125
DISPATCHER: (ON RADIO)
You got it, Mare.

50:37.375 --> 50:38.750
(INHALES)

51:06.291 --> 51:09.000
