51:19.792 --> 51:21.291
What are you doing up?

51:22.125 --> 51:24.333
Uh, my legs
are acting up again.

51:25.417 --> 51:27.917
I feel like I got ants
crawling through 'em.

51:29.125 --> 51:30.542
Don't ever get old.

51:31.125 --> 51:32.583
What's your excuse?

51:33.041 --> 51:34.333
My excuse?

51:36.291 --> 51:38.917
For walking in
at 3:30 in the morning.

51:39.000 --> 51:40.917
-(PILLS RATTLING)
-(SCOFFS) Hey.

51:42.041 --> 51:45.375
You're living in my house now,
remember?

51:46.583 --> 51:48.041
The hell's that
supposed to mean?

51:48.125 --> 51:52.625
(SIGHS) It means
I can come home at 3:30 a.m.,

51:52.709 --> 51:56.417
drunk, high,
or sideways if I want to,

51:56.500 --> 51:58.959
and not be made to feel
I'm a fool.

51:59.041 --> 52:01.250
Oh, well, good for you, Mare.

52:03.583 --> 52:05.375
Yeah. It is good for me.

52:07.834 --> 52:09.917
HELEN: You're a lot of things
I don't like,

52:10.542 --> 52:12.125
but you're not a fool.

52:15.583 --> 52:17.959
(TOILET FLUSHES)

52:18.667 --> 52:19.583
Hey.

52:19.667 --> 52:21.333
You get it all out, buddy?

52:21.417 --> 52:23.583
-Yes.
-MARE: Okay. Come on. Let's go.

52:27.959 --> 52:30.834
Gran, can you rub my head?

52:30.917 --> 52:32.083
MARE: Mm-hmm.

52:34.250 --> 52:35.750
Okay. In you get.

52:37.792 --> 52:39.375
Come on. Up.

52:40.792 --> 52:46.000
I named my turtle Kevin
because my dad was named Kevin.

52:46.875 --> 52:50.125
-Oh.
-Did my dad also like turtles?

52:51.250 --> 52:55.583
(SIGHS) He did. Yeah.

52:56.709 --> 52:58.125
(DREW EXHALES)

52:58.875 --> 53:00.959
Come on. Look at your stars.

53:06.375 --> 53:10.125
♪ ("POCKETS OF LIGHT"
BY LUBOMYR MELNYK PLAYING) ♪

53:22.792 --> 53:24.500
(SIGHS)

53:43.166 --> 53:46.208
(CRYING)

53:57.375 --> 53:59.834
(CRYING CONTINUES)

